{"tid":1573120,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"生仔應如岳義士，嫁郎應嫁岳義士，勇武應如岳義士","createTime":"2019-09-16T01:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T00:58:32.000Z","uid":77277,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e8da80aad0c9d051f5cb558cd1cdd061837a4838","tid":1573120,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:27:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">岳仔</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3abb811edc0e1dcf93a8b1cba97defe0752f812","tid":1573120,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T01:31:06.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"14e5e86477b52596c5cb9d2b21bba6dd5e489ea4","tid":1573120,"uid":283494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T00:58:32.000Z","msg":"唐朝已經推崇勇武，有詩為證。<br />\n<br />\n俠客行<br />\n~~李白<br />\n<br />\n趙客縵胡纓，吳鉤霜雪明。銀鞍照白馬，颯沓如流星。<br />\n(俠士出發前要裝備全身)<br />\n<br />\n十步殺一人，千里不留行。事了拂衣去，深藏身與名。<br />\n(快狠準)<br />\n<br />\n閑過信陵飲，脫劍膝前橫。將炙啖朱亥，持觴勸侯嬴。<br />\n(閑時，把酒談心做文宣)<br />\n<br />\n三杯吐然諾，五嶽倒為輕。眼花耳熱後，意氣素霓生。<br />\n<br />\n救趙揮金槌，邯鄲先震驚。千秋二壯士，煊赫大梁城。<br />\n(勁呀!)<br />\n<br />\n縱死俠骨香，不慚世上英。誰能書閣下，白首太玄經。<br />\n(千古傳誦)"}]}